<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1436,1586,1755]" pageId="8" pageNumber="149">
<number box="[151,168,1587,1611]" pageId="8" pageNumber="149" value="2.0">2</number>
. The photos of 
<taxonomicName box="[386,543,1586,1611]" class="Insecta" family="Hemiptera" genus="Brachyplatys" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="149" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="subaeneus">
<emphasis box="[386,543,1586,1611]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="149">B. subaeneus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
provided by 
<bibRefCitation author="Tomokuni" box="[716,916,1586,1611]" pageId="8" pageNumber="149" refString="Tomokuni, M. (Ed.) (1993) A field guide to Japanese bugs. Terrestrial heteropterans. Zenkoku Noson Kyoiku Kyokai, Tokyo, 380 pp. [in Japanese]" type="book" year="1993">
Tomokuni (
<number box="[855,916,1587,1611]" pageId="8" pageNumber="149" value="1993.0">1993</number>
</bibRefCitation>
: plate 
<number box="[1004,1032,1587,1611]" pageId="8" pageNumber="149" value="83.0">83</number>
figs. 
<number box="[1112,1155,1586,1611]" pageId="8" pageNumber="149" value="252.0">252</number>
a–b) are also based on misidentification and pertain to 
<taxonomicName box="[583,685,1622,1647]" class="Insecta" family="Hemiptera" genus="Brachyplatys" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="149" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vahlii">
<emphasis box="[583,685,1622,1647]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="149">B. vahlii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Japanese records of 
<taxonomicName box="[952,1106,1622,1647]" class="Insecta" family="Hemiptera" genus="Brachyplatys" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="149" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="subaeneus">
<emphasis box="[952,1106,1622,1647]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="149">B. subaeneus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
after 
<bibRefCitation author="Tomokuni" box="[1185,1388,1622,1647]" pageId="8" pageNumber="149" refString="Tomokuni, M. (Ed.) (1993) A field guide to Japanese bugs. Terrestrial heteropterans. Zenkoku Noson Kyoiku Kyokai, Tokyo, 380 pp. [in Japanese]" type="book" year="1993">
Tomokuni (
<number box="[1321,1379,1623,1647]" pageId="8" pageNumber="149" value="1993.0">1993</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
are potentially based on this work and therefore might represent misidentifications too; at least the record of 
<bibRefCitation author="Hosokawa" box="[199,461,1694,1719]" pageId="8" pageNumber="149" refString="Hosokawa, T., Kikuchi, Y. Nikoh, N., Shimada, M. &amp; Fukatsu, T. (2006) Strict host-symbiont cospeciation and reductive genome evolution in insect gut bacteria. PloS Biology, 4 (10), 1841 - 1851. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.1371 / journal. pbio. 0040337" type="journal article" year="2006">
Hosokawa 
<emphasis box="[325,383,1694,1719]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="149">et al.</emphasis>
(
<number box="[399,461,1694,1719]" pageId="8" pageNumber="149" value="2006.0">2006</number>
</bibRefCitation>
: 
<number box="[473,532,1695,1719]" pageId="8" pageNumber="149" value="1842.0">1842</number>
, fig. 
<number box="[590,600,1695,1719]" pageId="8" pageNumber="149" value="1.0">1</number>
C) pertains to 
<taxonomicName box="[768,865,1694,1719]" class="Insecta" family="Hemiptera" genus="Brachyplatys" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="149" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vahlii">
<emphasis box="[768,865,1694,1719]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="149">B. vahlii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<bibRefCitation author="Yamashita" box="[880,1223,1694,1719]" pageId="8" pageNumber="149" refString="Yamashita, I. &amp; Kikuhara, Y. (2012) Family Plataspidae Dallas, 1851. In: Ishikawa, T., Takai, M. &amp; Yasunaga, T. (Eds.), A field guide to Japanese bugs-Terrestrial heteropterans. Vol. 3. Zenkoku Noson Kyoiku Kyokai Publishing Co., Tokyo, pp. 439 - 444, plates 102 - 103. [in Japanese]" type="book chapter" year="2012">
Yamashita &amp; Kikuhara (
<number box="[1156,1215,1695,1719]" pageId="8" pageNumber="149" value="2012.0">2012</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Nagashima" pageId="8" pageNumber="149" refString="Nagashima, S &amp; Tanaka, Y. (2014) A new distributional record of Brachyplatys vahlii (Heteroptera, Plataspidae) from Ishigakijima Island of the Ryukyus, Japan. Rostria, 56, 51 - 52. [in Japanese]" type="journal article" year="2014">
Nagashima &amp; Tanaka (
<number box="[294,353,1731,1755]" pageId="8" pageNumber="149" value="2014.0">2014</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
identified both species correctly.
</paragraph>
